Texts.Chs: 有许许多多的事情是一个人无法逃避的。你自己。你的过去。改变。时间。黑洞穿过视界后的引力。幸运的是，这里没有黑洞，所以我没事。完全没事...
Texts.Eng: There are all to many things one cannot escape from. Yourself. Your past. Change. Time. The gravitational pull of a black hole after passing through the event horizon. Luckily, there's no black hole here, so I'm fine. Totally fine...
